## File Structure
```
cryptoAnalysisPages/
├── smart-dashboard-with-donations.html  # Main dashboard with themes (v2.2)
├── smart-dashboard.html                 # Previous version (v1.8)
├── assets/
│   ├── css/dashboard.css               # Console-style styling with themes and collapsible sections
│   ├── js/app.js                      # Dashboard functionality with theme management and enhanced fallback logic
│   └── pairs/                         # Trading pair data and charts
├── config/
│   ├── pairs.json                     # Pair configuration
│   └── donate.js                      # Donation configuration
└── tracking                           # This development tracking file
```

